Forever shall I be. wrote:
> The problem was with the checksum code, IIRC..
Ah. Now I remember: the old ping calculates the checksum incorrectly,
so the machine who is supposed to reply discards the ping-packet
without responding, if it correctly verifies the checksum before
replying.
